&lt;p&gt;This is a PR merged from a forked repository.&lt;br/&gt;
As GitHub hides the original diff on merge, it is displayed below for&lt;br/&gt;
the sake of provenance:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As this is a foreign pull request (from a fork), the diff is supplied&lt;br/&gt;
below (as it won&apos;t show otherwise due to GitHub magic):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;diff --git a/tools/releasing/create_source_release.sh b/tools/releasing/create_source_release.sh&lt;br/&gt;
index 93298027cbc..47b21768614 100755&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;#8212; a/tools/releasing/create_source_release.sh&lt;br/&gt;
+++ b/tools/releasing/create_source_release.sh&lt;br/&gt;
@@ -70,7 +70,8 @@ rsync -a \&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; tar czf ${RELEASE_DIR}/flink-${RELEASE_VERSION}&lt;del&gt;src.tgz flink&lt;/del&gt;$RELEASE_VERSION&lt;br/&gt;
 gpg -&lt;del&gt;armor --detach-sig ${RELEASE_DIR}/flink&lt;/del&gt;$RELEASE_VERSION-src.tgz&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;del&gt;$SHASUM ${RELEASE_DIR}/flink&lt;/del&gt;$RELEASE_VERSION-src.tgz &amp;gt; ${RELEASE_DIR}/flink-$RELEASE_VERSION-src.tgz.sha512&lt;br/&gt;
+cd ${RELEASE_DIR}&lt;br/&gt;
+$SHASUM flink-$RELEASE_VERSION-src.tgz &amp;gt; flink-$RELEASE_VERSION-src.tgz.sha512&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; cd ${CURR_DIR}&lt;br/&gt;
 rm -rf ${CLONE_DIR}&lt;/p&gt;




